caveats: The source data includes administrative level 2 features 'CHITATO' and 'LÓVUA' in administrative level 1 feature "LUNDA NORTE" [AO12] that are represented together as "CHITAO-LÓVUA" [AO12104] in the COD-AB.  Therefore the spreadsheet contains an extra tab "ago_admpop_adm2_AO12104_2022" providing the two records for that feature.  Only the "ago_admpop_adm2_2022" tab is provided as a CSV file.
